title: #TOURNOTES: US OPEN OF SURFING 2013
description: Lots of friends, dust and action. Congrats to Alejo Muniz, Carissa Moore, Conner Coffin, Kolohe Andino, Curren Caples, Greyson Fletcher and all the other Hurley athletes who made last week so fun to watch. See more from our team at http://hurley.com/athletes.
